    <h2>HURICANE IRENE -<span class="redText"> ARE YOU READY?</span></h2>
    <p><u></u>The threat level from the eastern N.C. to southern New England is <strong class="redText"><u>extreme</u></strong>. The potential for widespread damaging winds, flooding rain, and, in some locations, coastal flooding and storm surge is <strong><u>very real</u></strong> this weekend.</p>
<p><strong>Stay informed.</strong><strong> </strong>Continue to follow-up the news on CNN - <a href="http://www.cnn.com" target="_blank" class="BLinks">www.cnn.com</a> and The Weather Channel - <a href="http://www.weather.com" target="_blank" class="BLinks">www.weather.com</a> and National Hurricane center - <a href="http://www.nhc.noaa.gov" target="_blank" class="BLinks">www.nhc.noaa.gov</a></p>
    <p><strong>Listen to the authorities and follow their instructions</strong>. Some local communities may order mandatory evacuation.</p>
    <p><strong>Seek shelter, if needed.</strong> Local authorities or the Red Cross may organize storm shelters for your  safety. If there is a shelter available and the hurricane will be in  your area, go there for your safety.</p>
    <p>Prepare yourself. </strong><strong>Make sure you have a &ldquo;To Go&rdquo; bag ready. Do NOT forget:</u></strong></p>
    <ul>
    <li><strong>Take important documents with YOU.</strong> This includes passport, Form DS-2019, Form I-94, medical card, Social  Security Card, Financial Records, plane ticket, checks, credit cards, etc)</li>
    <li><strong>Take contact numbers and e-mail address. </strong>Please stay in touch with CSB: <a href="tel:1-877-669-0717" value="+18776690717" target="_blank" class="BLinks">1-877-669-0717</a> (dial 0 for the operator), <a href="mailto:info@csb-usa.com" target="_blank" class="BLinks">info@csb-usa.com</a></li>
    <li><strong>Contact your family members to let them know they are safe and how they can be reached.</strong></li>
    <li><strong>Take SEVP and Department of State contact information with you</strong>. SEVP email address: <a href="mailto:SEVIS.Source@dhs.gov" target="_blank" class="BLinks">SEVIS.Source@dhs.gov.;</a> Department of State e-mail address: <a href="mailto:Jvisas@state.gov" target="_blank" class="BLinks">Jvisas@state.gov</a>.</li></ul>
    
    <p>CSB International, Inc. is here to assist if you have questions: <a href="tel:1-877-669-0717" value="+18776690717" target="_blank" class="BLinks">1-877-669-0717</a> (dial 0 for the operator). <strong>IF YOU ARE IN DANGER, PLEASE CALL 911.</strong></p>
